Class Client

  • java.lang.Object
    • Client
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Client>

    public class Client
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Client>
    The Client class is used to represent a clients who attend a World Sports Championship. The class holds the First and Last name of the client along with a list of events they are attending.
    Author:
    Andrew Brown
